after doing this: ``` {% set TableID = [ID] %}
{% set table_info = hubdb_table_rows(TableID) %}
          counter {{ table_info.row_count }} ``` I don't get any results and I get a warning that ` cannot resolve property row_count in `

Doing it in hubdb_table would get you the number of total rows though, and wouldn't account for any filters. If you need the filtered number of rows, you can do
```{% set rows = hubdb_table_rows(tableID, query) %}
{{ rows|count }}```
